snippet.title: Crazy Guy Storms Barstool HQ Threatening To Sue + Abella Danger Returns - Stool Scenes 228.5
snippet.description:
Reminder: We are giving you 2 brand new episodes of Stool Scenes each week! Please continue to like, comment and subscribe! 

Many people have stormed Barstool HQ uninvited & talking crazy but what transpired on Friday afternoon is tough to put into words. #ElPres did a pretty good job of it with his blog and this episode should be able to do the rest. We also show some of the madness this past weekend in Buffalo with #BillsMafia, talk about the absolute atrocity of a crime committed by that rat fuck JMac3 + YP makes a fantasy become a reality with #AbellaDanger.
